                <h1>Can Employers Access Your Medical Card Information?</h1>
                <p>Employers generally cannot see if you have a medical card due to privacy laws, such as HIPAA in the U.S. This act protects your medical information, making it illegal for employers to access your medical records without consent. Always check local laws as regulations may vary.</p>
